Type: Package
Package: cephalopod
Title: Access the Kraken API
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Dennis",
           family = "Mayk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dennis@mayk.eu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5017-1495"))
Description: A framework to trade cryptocurrencies using the Kraken API <https://api.kraken.com> that provides functions to obtain OHLC data for different asset pairs, retrieve information about open and closed orders, submit or cancel orders, and gain insights into Kraken's order book.  
License: AGPL (>= 3)
